==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Noun===
'''limestone'''
#{{mineralogy}} An abundant [[rock]] of [[marine]] and fresh-water [[sediment]]s; primarily composed of [[calcite]] (CaCO₃); it occurs in a variety of forms, both [[crystal]]line and [[amorphous]].  
[[Image:Pflimestone.jpg|frame|Limestone, [[amorphous]] and [[fossiliferous]]. Photos US Geological Survey]]
